(3, 'Best Laptops Under 50,000 in Nepal', 'best-laptops-under-50000-in-nepal', 'Do you want a laptop that best suits you but at an affordable price? Heres a list of notebooks with their specifications that is available under 50k in Nepal. The laptops mentioned are from the middle range to the best in Nepal.', '<h2><strong>#1. Lenovo Ideapad 330</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Lenovo Ideapad 330 core i3 8th gen comes with 15.6&rsquo;&rsquo; HD, and Integrated GFX costs you Rs. 45,500.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Details of Lenovo Ideapad 330:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Model: Lenovo Ideapad 330-15lKB</li>\r\n<li>Display: 15.6 inch</li>\r\n<li>Dimension: 37.8 x 26 x 2.3 cm</li>\r\n<li>Weight: 2.2kg</li>\r\n<li>Operating system: Windows 10</li>\r\n<li>Generation: 8th Gen</li>\r\n<li>Processor: Intel Core i3 (8th Gen)</li>\r\n<li>Graphics: Integrated GFX</li>\r\n<li>RAM: 4 GB</li>\r\n<li>Hard Drive Size: 1024GB</li>\r\n<li>Battery: 2 cell Li-ion battery</li>\r\n<li>Color: Platinum Grey</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 2.0 Ports: 2</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 3.0 Ports: 1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>#2. Acer Aspire E15 i5-8250U</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Acer Aspire E15 with Intel Core i5 (8th Gen) costs you Rs.49,500 in Nepal. It comes with 8 GB RAM and one year warranty.</p>\r\n<h3>Specification:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Model: Acer Aspire E15</li>\r\n<li>Display: 15.6 inch (1920 x 1080 Pixel)</li>\r\n<li>Dimension: 15 x 10.2 x 1.2 inches</li>\r\n<li>Weight: 5.27 pounds</li>\r\n<li>Operating system: Windows 10</li>\r\n<li>Generation: 8th Gen</li>\r\n<li>Processor: Intel Core i5 (8th Gen)</li>\r\n<li>Graphics: AMD Radeon 520</li>\r\n<li>RAM: 8 GB</li>\r\n<li>Storage: 256GB SSD</li>\r\n<li>Battery: 4 cell Li-ion battery</li>\r\n<li>Color: Obsidian Black</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong># 3.Dell Inspiron 15 3567</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Dell has provided its users with various ranges of laptops. Dell Inspiron 3567 is an affordable high performing laptop that will cost you Rs.45,999. Dell Inspiron 15 3567 comes with Intel Core i3 processor, Intel HD graphics. 4GB RAM and 1TB HDD CApacity.The 15.6&rsquo;&rsquo; display laptop comes with a one year warranty.</p>\r\n<p>Specification of Dell Inspiron 3567:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Model: Dell Inspiron 3567</li>\r\n<li>Display: 15.6 inch</li>\r\n<li>Size: Height: 23.3mm (0.92) x Width: 390mm (15.35) x Depth: 259mm (10.20)</li>\r\n<li>Operating system: Windows 10</li>\r\n<li>Generation: 7th Gen</li>\r\n<li>Processor: Intel Core i3 (7th Gen)</li>\r\n<li>Graphics: Intel HD</li>\r\n<li>RAM: 4 GB</li>\r\n<li>HDD Capacity: 1TB</li>\r\n<li>Battery: 42 WHr, Prismatic 2-Cell Battery (integrated)</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 2.0 Ports: 1</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 3.0 Ports: 2</li>\r\n<li>HDMI port: 1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>4.Acer Aspire E14</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Acer Aspire E14 costs Rs.44,000 in Nepal. The high performing laptop comes with a one year warranty with Intel Core i3 processor. The display is 14&rsquo;&rsquo; HD Display with 335 x 227 x20 mm dimension.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Specification of Acer Aspire E14:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Model: Acer Aspire E14</li>\r\n<li>Dimension: 335 x 227 x 20 mm</li>\r\n<li>Display: 14 inches, HD display</li>\r\n<li>Weight: 2.1kg</li>\r\n<li>Operating system: Windows 10</li>\r\n<li>Generation: 7th Gen</li>\r\n<li>Processor: Intel Core i3 (8th Gen)</li>\r\n<li>Graphics: Intel UHD 620</li>\r\n<li>RAM: 4 GB</li>\r\n<li>HDD Capacity: 1TB</li>\r\n<li>Battery: 42 WHr, Prismatic 2-Cell Battery (integrated)</li>\r\n<li>Color: Black</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 2.0 Ports: 1</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 3.0 Ports: 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><strong>#5. Lenovo V130</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Lenovo V130 comes with a 15.6&rsquo;&rsquo; HD LED Backlit AntiGlare Display. At Rs 39,999/- you will get this high-performance laptop with Intel Core i3-7020U 7th Gen Intel Processor. It comes with a warranty of 1 year.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Lenovo V130 Specifications:</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Model: Lenovo V130</li>\r\n<li>Display: 15.6 inches (1366 x 768 Pixels), HD LED Backlit AntiGlare Display</li>\r\n<li>Dimension: 375 x 253 x 22.3 mm</li>\r\n<li>Weight: 2.73kg</li>\r\n<li>Operating system: Windows 10</li>\r\n<li>Generation: 7th Gen</li>\r\n<li>Processor: Intel Core i3-7020U (7th Gen)</li>\r\n<li>Graphics: Intel HD 620</li>\r\n<li>RAM: 4 GB</li>\r\n<li>HDD Capacity: 1TB</li>\r\n<li>Battery: 2 cell Li-Po battery</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 2.0 Ports: 1</li>\r\n<li>Number of USB 3.0 Ports: 2</li>\r\n<li>HDMI Port: 1</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 'publish', 15, 'Blog-20200826011910738.jpg', '2020-08-26 07:34:10', '2020-08-26 07:34:10'),
(4, 'NEPALESE PEOPLE AND LIFESTYLE', 'nepalese-people-and-lifestyle', 'Unity, even in diversity has been the hallmark of Nepali society and it must be preserved.', '<p><span>People in Nepal commonly welcome you by Namaste as a traditional salute (means I salute the divine in you) which is widely used in the most part of country. About 23 million Nepalese are made of 69 different cultural and linguistic group also known as ethnic groups living in different, regions of the country. Mostly each ethnic group has their own unique costumes, speak their own languages or dialects, and follow their own religious practices. They live under different diverse geographic and ecological orientations, from the low plains near the Indian border, northward through the middle hills of Mahabharat range and valleys, and up to the high plain valleys of the Himalayan zone.</span><br /><br /><span>However globalization has pushed innovation effects to the Nepalese society which has brought many infrastructural developments like extension of roads, new buildings, modern education system, rapid innovation of information technology and Internet access. More and more Nepalese, especially young folks speak Nepali and fluent English language, dresses western style clothes most of the time and generally relate to the outside world.</span><br /><br /><span>Unity, even in diversity has been the hallmark of Nepali society and it must be preserved. The most effective way of doing this is to adopt a multi-ethnic basis to federalism. Though Nepal is a veritable mosaic of dozens of ethnic groups, they are bound together by their loyalty to the institution of Monarchy, and by the ideas of peaceful coexistence and religious tolerance to form one unified nation.</span></p>', 0, 'publish', 18, 'Blog-20200826012721964.jpg', '2020-08-26 07:42:21', '2020-08-26 07:42:21'),
